description:
I woke up crying this morning, just KNOWING that something terrible had happened. At first I ignored the feeling... but I JUST KNEW. And I was right. Later that day, on a cold afternoon, I went online to watch some SU shit and that's where I would find out that a famous actor... one that was in an episode of Sonic Underground.. had died. 
Luke Parry was a huge fan of Sonic Underround, so much so that he requested to be featured in an episode, which the creators of Sonic underground graciously accepted! Unfortunately he passed today... but his memory lives on through Sonic Underground! This tribute goes out to his family and loved ones
